  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/739010/extras/ad51b83e1b7957dd6803ab8971d56b91.webp?t=1600788120\" width=600 height=46 /></span><br><strong>The Blue Box</strong> is host to a collection of individually purchasable games:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Make burgers with physics to earn minimum wage in <strong>BurgerGame</strong>.<br></li><li> Negotiate the price of food items as a llama in <strong>Llama goes to Market</strong>.<br></li><li> Realize the full extent of humanity in <strong>YWDH</strong>.<br></li><li> Race against other ostriches to escape the police in <strong>DDAFPST Ostriches</strong>.<br></li><li> Play basketball across the globe in <strong>BBA SLAM</strong>.<br></li><li> Go back in time to snap some sweet pics of creatures in <strong>Oligocene Snapshot</strong>.<br></li><li> Pilot a futuristic jet at breakneck speeds through a sci-fi city in <strong>Normality</strong>.</li></ul><br><strong>The Blue Box</strong> is also host to a gallery of toys and other completely free game experiments:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Raise your virtual forever friend in <strong>Pocket Dootie</strong>.<br></li><li> Live a day in the life of a fabric weaving friend in <strong>Pube Spider (I Love You)</strong>.</li></ul><br>More and more games are being added over time, thanks to everyone's support.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/739010/extras/ad51b83e1b7957dd6803ab8971d56b91.webp?t=1600788120\" width=600 height=46 /></span><br><strong>The Blue Box</strong> is host to a collection of individually purchasable games:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Make burgers with physics to earn minimum wage in <strong>BurgerGame</strong>.<br></li><li> Negotiate the price of food items as a llama in <strong>Llama goes to Market</strong>.<br></li><li> Realize the full extent of humanity in <strong>YWDH</strong>.<br></li><li> Race against other ostriches to escape the police in <strong>DDAFPST Ostriches</strong>.<br></li><li> Play basketball across the globe in <strong>BBA SLAM</strong>.<br></li><li> Go back in time to snap some sweet pics of creatures in <strong>Oligocene Snapshot</strong>.<br></li><li> Pilot a futuristic jet at breakneck speeds through a sci-fi city in <strong>Normality</strong>.</li></ul><br><strong>The Blue Box</strong> is also host to a gallery of toys and other completely free game experiments:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Raise your virtual forever friend in <strong>Pocket Dootie</strong>.<br></li><li> Live a day in the life of a fabric weaving friend in <strong>Pube Spider (I Love You)</strong>.</li></ul><br>More and more games are being added over time, thanks to everyone's support.",
